        "description": "This game is a VR escape game.\nSolve the mysteries in each stage and uncover the hidden truth.\nArchaeology has never been more challenging!\nFind yourselves locked in an ancient Egyptian tomb with puzzles and surprises that can lead to your freedom.\nPay attention to what surrounds you and find the solution to the puzzles!\n\n[Menu Interact Button: Right or Left Trigger]\nFeatures:\nPlayer Movement:\nStick Movement And/Or Teleport\nInventory System:\n[Y Button] Check Your Items, Documents etc...\nInGame Menu:\n[Left Menu Button]Change Your Settings while you are playing.\nGrab:\n[Right/Left Trigger]Distance Grab The Object, use the relative stick to get the object closer and grab it.\nSave And Load:\nProgress are saved at the start and end of a level.\nEquip Item\n[A or X Button] Select The equipped item from inventory.\n\nIf you find bugs or inconsistencies while playing, do not hesitate to contact us via the form on our site!",
